      <description><![CDATA[ <h3>ParkShelf 1.0.3</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Auto-doze fix:</strong> the shelf now collapses to its compact puck after a few seconds idle <em>even when pinned</em>. Pinning now only locks the shelf's position &mdash; it no longer keeps it expanded.</li>
  <li><strong>New appearances:</strong> pick <strong>Liquid Glass</strong> or <strong>Liquid Glass Clear</strong> alongside the standard look, with <strong>Translucency</strong> and <strong>Tint</strong> sliders to fine-tune the glass (Settings &rarr; ParkShelf).</li>
  <li><strong>Consistent preview:</strong> the live-preview panel now matches your chosen appearance.</li>
</ul> ]]></description>
